name: The Queen's Dreams: Ethereal Palace
description:
Their soft celestial voices filled the space.
Their brushed red lips did not move and the sound was sheer vibration.
The tone, pitch perfect and true noise of heavens kind.
They flocked around her.
Rank meant nothing in her presence.
They only wished to see her light.
She sang.
A song of only day dreams and lucid thoughts.
Arms open, she beckoned and she called.
Come home Dear Ones.
For here you are always Loved.
And so they came.
In their droves they flew, wings spread wide. 
This was now or never.
Be here with her forever. The choice was the simplest for them to make.
In this moment they were undying and blessed.
The golden gates sealed firmly behind all those who entered.
Fear was a fallacy and it belonged in them no more.
